label: Cumulative person-time
definition: Person time contributed by the child

label: Census timepoint
definition: Timepoint: beginning of census interval or end of census interval

label: Trial phase
definition: MORDOR I is phase 1-4, MORDOR II is 5-6 and MORDOR III is phase 7-10.

label: Cluster trial phase
definition: MORDOR I is phase 1-4, MORDOR II is 5-6.

label: Died
definition: Indicator of child mortality, recorded at end census

label: Moved during census interval
